Good challenge, I approve.

My solluce in `php` :

```php
<?php

function isLetter($char) {
    return preg_match('/^([\A-Za-z])+$/', $char);
}

function isUppercase($char) {
    return preg_match('/^([\A-Z])+$/', $char);
}

$recipe = str_split(stream_get_line(STDIN, 4 + 1, "\n"));

$start = $recipe[0];
unset($recipe[0]);

$step = $recipe[1];
unset($recipe[1]);

$length = implode('', $recipe);

$array = !isLetter($start) 
            ? range(0, 9)
            : (isUppercase($start) 
                ? range('A', 'Z')
                : range('a', 'z'));

$start = array_search($start, $array);
$step = array_search($step, $array);

$dir = $step - $start;

for($i = 1; $i<=$length; $i++) {
    for($j = 0; $j < $i; $j ++) {
        echo $array[$start];
    }

    $start += $dir;
    if($start >= count($array)) {
        $start -= count($array);
    } elseif($start < 0) {
        $start += count($array);
    }

    echo PHP_EOL;
}
```
